Code for Paper "Joint Factual and Counterfactual Explanations for Top-$k$ GNN-based Recommendations"

This repository contains the code to preprocess datasets, train GNN models, and jointly find the factual and counterfactual explanation of gnn-based recommender
manuscript "Joint Factual and Counterfactual Explanations for Top-$k$ GNN-based Recommendations"


pip -r install pip.txt

python Joint_Perturb.py --alpha 0.03 --beta 0.01
